OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,FThe Body Shop has entered
OL,7,Fadministration after poor sales across
OL,8,Fthe Christmas shopping season
OL,10,FThe UK arm of The Body Shop has
OL,11,Fentered into administration, leaving
OL,12,Fthousands of jobs at risk, it has been
OL,13,Fconfirmed.
OL,15,FInsolvency experts at FRP Advisory
OL,16,Fhave been brought in to oversee the
OL,17,Fadministration process after poor
OL,18,Fsales during the Christmas shopping
OL,19,Fseason continued into January.
