OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,FA source close to Aurelius told ITV
OL,7,FNews that The Body Shop sits in a "far
OL,8,Fworse financial state" than it had
OL,9,Fanticipated when it acquired the brand.
OL,11,FThe retailer was founded in 1976 by
OL,12,FAnita Roddick and her husband Gordon
OL,13,Fas one of the first companies to
OL,14,Fpromote so-called ethical consumerism,
OL,15,Ffocusing on ethically produced
OL,16,Fcosmetics and skincare products.
