OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,FSpeaking about the move to appoint
OL,7,Fadministrators amid financial
OL,8,Fdifficulty being faced by the
OL,9,Fcosmetics chain, ITV News Economics
OL,10,FEditor Joel Hills said: "Plan A will
OL,11,Fbe to find a buyer for the business in
OL,12,Fits current form.
OL,14,F"And, on the face of it, that seems
OL,15,Flike a pretty tall order but we don't
OL,16,Fknow how loss making The Body Shop is
OL,17,Fand we don't know how much debt it is
OL,18,Fcarrying around.
