OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,F"One important detail is that Aurelius
OL,7,Fhas a security over a part of The Body
OL,8,FShop's debt, which means Aurelius is a
OL,9,Fcreditor as well as an owner of the
OL,10,Fbusiness. Something that will give the
OL,11,Ffirm leverage and influence over the
OL,12,Finsolvency process.
OL,14,F"That may well mean that the
OL,15,Fadministrator ends up cutting costs by
OL,16,Fclosing shops and making people
OL,17,Fredundant, renegotiating contracts
OL,18,Fwith landlords and then handing the
OL,19,Fbusiness back to Aurelius."
