OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,FLush chief executive, Mark Constantine
OL,7,Ftold Joel Hills: "The business will
OL,8,Fsurvive in some shape or form, but it
OL,9,Fis probable that half the network of
OL,10,Fshops will close."
OL,12,FIn a statement, The Body Shop said:
OL,13,F"Taking this approach, provides the
OL,14,Fstability, flexibility and security to
OL,15,Ffind the best means of securing the
OL,16,Ffuture of The Body Shop and
OL,17,Frevitalizing this iconic British brand.
