OL,3,CThe Body Shop goes into administration
OL,4,Cleaving thousands of jobs at risk
OL,6,F"The Joint Administrators will now
OL,7,Fconsider all options to find a way
OL,8,Fforward for the business and will
OL,9,Fupdate creditors and employees in due
OL,10,Fcourse.
OL,12,F"Creating a more nimble and
OL,13,Ffinancially stable UK business, is an
OL,14,Fimportant step in achieving this.
OL,16,F"The Joint Administrators will
OL,17,Fcontinue to trade the business in
OL,18,Fadministration, ensuring customers
OL,19,Fwill be able to continue to shop in
OL,20,Fstore and online for their favourite
OL,21,Fproducts."
