OL,7,Ffacing an "extended period of
OL,8,Ffinancial challenges" under past
OL,9,Fowners, that pushed Aurelius to close
OL,10,FThe Body Shop at Home and sell
OL,11,Fbusinesses across Europe and Asia.
OL,13,FThe business employed around 10,000
OL,14,Fpeople worldwide at the time of the
OL,15,Ftakeover.
